l Thunak''\n| Flutist\n|-\n|rowspan= 1|1979\n| ''Akke Mata Awasara''\n| \n|-\n|rowspan= 1|1979\n| ''Subhani''\n|\n|-\n|rowspan= 1|1979\n| ''Nuwan Renu''\n| Pabilis\n|-\n|rowspan= 1|1979\n| ''Wisihathara Peya''\n| \n|-\n|rowspan= 1|1979\n| ''Hari Pudumai''\n| \n|-\n|rowspan= 1|1980\n| ''Silva''\n| \n|-\n|rowspan= 1|1980\n| ''Muwan Pelessa 2''\n| Pina\n|-\n|rowspan= 1|1980\n| ''Adara Rathne''\n| Student leader \n|-\n|rowspan= 1|1981\n| ''Kolam Karayo''\n| Ahanga Lal Sulojana\n|-\n|rowspan= 1|1981\n| ''Geethika''\n| Silva 'Mahathaya' \n|-\n|rowspan= 1|1981\n| ''Anjaana''\n| \n|-\n|rowspan= 1|1981\n| ''Ek Dawasak Ra''\n| Photographer\n|-\n|rowspan= 1|1981\n| ''Amme Mata Samawenna''\n| Freddie\n|-\n|rowspan= 1|1982\n| ''Miss Mallika 1982''\n| \n|-\n|rowspan= 1|1982\n| ''Wathura Karaththaya''\n| Reporter\n|-\n|rowspan= 1|1982\n| ''[[Kadawunu Poronduwa (1982 film)|Kadawunu Poronduwa remake]]''\n| Sewaris 'Unnah'\n|-\n|rowspan= 1|1983\n| ''Sumithuro''\n| \n|-\n|rowspan= 1|1983\n| ''Chandi Siriya''\n| \n|-\n|rowspan= 1|1983\n| ''Sister Mary''\n| Friend\n|-\n|rowspan= 1|1983\n| ''Hasthi Viyaruwa''\n| Velu\n|-\n|rowspan= 1|1984\n| ''[[Ara Soyza]]''\n| Soyza\n|-\n|rowspan= 1|1984\n| ''Thaththai Puthai''\n| Silva\n|-\n|rowspan= 1|1984\n| ''Kakiley Rajjuruwo''\n| Andare\n|-\n|rowspan= 1|1985\n| ''Araliya Mal''\n| Bandara\n|-\n|rowspan= 1|1986\n| ''Dinuma''\n| Ustad\n|-\n|rowspan= 1|1986\n| ''Mal Varusa''\n| Lona\n|-\n|rowspan= 1|1987\n| ''Yugayen Yugayata''\n| \n|-\n|rowspan= 1|1987\n| ''Thaththi Man Adarei''\n| \n|-\n|rowspan= 1|1987\n| ''Yukthiyada Shakthiyada''\n| \n|-\n|rowspan= 1|1987\n| ''Raja Wedakarayo''\n| Upul 'Music Master' \n|-\n|rowspan= 1|1987\n| ''Ran Dam Wel''\n|  \n|-\n|rowspan= 1|1987\n| ''Obatai Priye Adare''\n| \n|-\n|rowspan= 1|1987\n| ''Ahinsa''\n| \n|-\n|rowspan= 1|1987\n| ''Hitha Honda Chandiya''\n| Serpino \n|-\n|rowspan= 1|1988\n| ''Newa Gilunath Bandchun''\n| Gira\n|-\n|rowspan= 1|1988\n| ''Rasa Rahasak''\n| Sena\n|-\n|rowspan= 1|1988\n| ''Gedara Budun 